OL,3,CFamily pet enjoying new lease of life
OL,4,Cas police dog in Nottinghamshire
OL,6,FA former family pet is embracing a new
OL,7,Flease of life as a qualified
OL,8,FNottinghamshire Police dog.
OL,10,FPD Riddick, was recruited last year
OL,11,Ffrom a specialist breeder and trainer
OL,12,Fin the West Midlands after his owners
OL,13,Fwere forced to give him up.
OL,15,FThe 18monthold Belgian Malinois
OL,16,Fcross, has just completed 13 weeks of
OL,17,Fintensive training and is now on
OL,18,Factive patrol with PC Chris Duffy.
