OL,3,CFamily pet enjoying new lease of life
OL,4,Cas police dog in Nottinghamshire
OL,6,FThe canine cop is trained to search
OL,7,Ffor people and property, track over
OL,8,Fground, detain people using force, and
OL,9,Fwork public order incidents.
OL,11,FPC Duffy said: "Riddick has shown
OL,12,Fhimself to be very good at criminal
OL,13,Fwork ` the chasing and running around
OL,14,F` and has also done very well at
OL,15,Fbuilding searches.
OL,17,F"He's only a young dog, but he's
OL,18,Freally got the potential to be a
OL,19,Ffantastic allrounder.
