OL,3,CFamily pet enjoying new lease of life
OL,4,Cas police dog in Nottinghamshire
OL,6,F"All in all, I'm just really pleased
OL,7,Fwe were able to give him this
OL,8,Fopportunity to put all his natural
OL,9,Fskills and instincts to such good use.
OL,11,F"As time goes on, I'm looking forward
OL,12,Fto developing our partnership further
OL,13,Fso we can best serve the public."
